descriptionHtml:
Shiina

[img]https://staticdelivery.nexusmods.com/mods/110/images/77237-1-1469041952.jpg[/img]

Race: Breton
Age: 17
Shiina is a magic user with a
fascination with conjuration magic. His
mother died of sickness, and he hasn't
seen his dad since he went off to fight
for the empire. Shiina is often moody 
like most teenagers, but he has a kind soul.

[u]Mods Used:[/u]
Hair:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/55364]Kijiko Hairs[/url] (required)
Face Texture:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/7887]Pretty Faces[/url] (for men)
Body Texture:[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/58443] Skysight body textures[/url]
Eye Texture:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13076]Cute Eyes[/url]
Outfit:  [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/44592]EotW Dovahkiins Journeyman Armor[/url]

This preset requires the [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]Racemenu [/url]mod.

How to Install:
Extract the contents of the zip file to the Skyrim folder.
author: MissChevus
